# Group Subscribers

## Subscriber [/subscriber/{id}{?token}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1234 (string)
    + token: AAABBBCCC (string, required)
    
+ Attributes (Subscriber Base)
    + id: 1234 (string, required)

### Retrieve a Subscriber [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber)

### Update a Subscriber [PUT]

+ Request Update a Subscriber (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber)
    
+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber)

### Delete a Subscriber [DELETE]

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber)

## Subscriber Collection [/subscriber{?token}]

+ Parameters
    + token: AAABBBCCC (string, required)
    
+ Attributes (Subscriber Base)

### New Subscriber [POST]

+ Request Create a Subscriber (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber Base)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Subscriber)

### List All Subscribers [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Subscriber])

